{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/rabbitmq3/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"JAVA 단기 심화 부트캠프","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">RabbitMQ</a></u>","src":null},"body":"<h2>전에 실습에 이어서..</h2>\n<p>전에 실습에서 그려봤던 아키텍처 이다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.12121212121212%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/c9b55/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 165w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/f2908/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 330w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/cc661/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 660w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/bc514/rabbitmq-drawio.webp 720w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/04c57/rabbitmq-drawio.png 165w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/d9ecf/rabbitmq-drawio.png 330w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/1f083/rabbitmq-drawio.png 660w,\n/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/37523/rabbitmq-drawio.png 720w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/810f0952a8e46d67f5f1abecc790db17/1f083/rabbitmq-drawio.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"RabbitMQ 아키텍처\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>RabbitMQ 아키텍처</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n전에 실습에서 그려봤던 아키텍처 이다. 오늘은 전에 포스팅에서도 말했었듯이 product application을 2개 생성하고 라운드 로빈형식으로 메세지를 받는 걸 실습을 해보겠다. 프로젝트는 전에 파일을 유지해서 진행했다.</p>\n<h2>Product Application 생성하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>start.spring.io에 접속해서 프로젝트를 생성하자</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/c9b55/product-spring-io.webp 165w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/f2908/product-spring-io.webp 330w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/cc661/product-spring-io.webp 660w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/a66df/product-spring-io.webp 990w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/d33d4/product-spring-io.webp 1320w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/f16bf/product-spring-io.webp 1371w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/04c57/product-spring-io.png 165w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/d9ecf/product-spring-io.png 330w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/1f083/product-spring-io.png 660w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/7a3d6/product-spring-io.png 990w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/78958/product-spring-io.png 1320w,\n/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/bb27a/product-spring-io.png 1371w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/dfc9255e2c6d4f1122b962bf5f47128e/1f083/product-spring-io.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Product Application\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Product Application</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>application.properties를 삭제하고 application.yml로 생성한뒤 다음과 같이 설정한다. 전에 payment 쪽에서 몇개만 수정하면 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">spring:\n  application:\n    name: product\n  rabbitmq:\n    host: localhost\n    port: 5672\n    username: guest\n    password: guest\nmessage:\n  queue:\n    product: market.product</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>ProductEndpoint.java 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import lombok.extern.slf4j.Slf4j;\nimport org.springframework.amqp.rabbit.annotation.RabbitListener;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Slf4j\n@Component\npublic class ProductEndpoint {\n\n    @Value(\"${spring.application.name}\")\n    private String appName;\n\n    @RabbitListener(queues = \"${message.queue.product}\")\n    public void receiveMessage(String orderId) {\n        log.info(\"receive orderId:{}, appName : {}\", orderId, appName);\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>구성편집 쪽에서 들어가서 기존 ProductApplication을 복제하고 옵션수정 쪽에서 VM설정을 클릭한 후 application.name옵션을 통해 구분하자\n<ul>\n<li>구성편집 > ProductApplication 복제 > 옵션수정 > add VM Option > -Dspring.application.name=product-1</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/c9b55/product-loadblancer.webp 165w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/f2908/product-loadblancer.webp 330w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/cc661/product-loadblancer.webp 660w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/b116a/product-loadblancer.webp 912w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/04c57/product-loadblancer.png 165w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/d9ecf/product-loadblancer.png 330w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/1f083/product-loadblancer.png 660w,\n/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/8b69f/product-loadblancer.png 912w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f29e0a1ee4d58b4fa39ecbb1f28267f1/1f083/product-loadblancer.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"옵션수정\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>옵션수정</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Product-1, Product-2 실행하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>이제 <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/order/1\">http://localhost:8080/order/1</a> 로 여러번 요청을 한 후 로그기록을 살펴보자</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">http://localhost:8080/order/1\nhttp://localhost:8080/order/2\nhttp://localhost:8080/order/3\nhttp://localhost:8080/order/4\nhttp://localhost:8080/order/5\nhttp://localhost:8080/order/6</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Product-1</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.63636363636364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/c9b55/log-product-1.webp 165w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/f2908/log-product-1.webp 330w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/cc661/log-product-1.webp 660w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/a66df/log-product-1.webp 990w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/d33d4/log-product-1.webp 1320w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/29105/log-product-1.webp 1396w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/04c57/log-product-1.png 165w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/d9ecf/log-product-1.png 330w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/1f083/log-product-1.png 660w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/7a3d6/log-product-1.png 990w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/78958/log-product-1.png 1320w,\n/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/58354/log-product-1.png 1396w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8141437fde252605f92cd47e8fc270dc/1f083/log-product-1.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Product-1 - log\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Product-1 - log</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Product-2</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.63636363636364%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/c9b55/log-product-2.webp 165w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/f2908/log-product-2.webp 330w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/cc661/log-product-2.webp 660w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/a66df/log-product-2.webp 990w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/d33d4/log-product-2.webp 1320w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/29105/log-product-2.webp 1396w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/04c57/log-product-2.png 165w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/d9ecf/log-product-2.png 330w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/1f083/log-product-2.png 660w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/7a3d6/log-product-2.png 990w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/78958/log-product-2.png 1320w,\n/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/58354/log-product-2.png 1396w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/93defb0fc4267f4607de2374153766ea/1f083/log-product-2.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Product-2 - log\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Product-2 - log</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>두개의 로그기록을 살펴보면 하나는 홀수번째만 다른 하나는 짝수번째만 찍힌걸 확인 할 수 있다. 이걸로 라운드 로빈 형식으로 잘 왔다는걸 확인 해볼수가 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>","categories":["RabbitMQ","TIL"],"date":"August 14, 2024","description":"JAVA 단기 심화 부트캠프","id":"efcc5497-6691-5ebe-876b-a4555e6a9f8e","keywords":["단기 심화 부트캠프","Sparta","RabbitMQ"],"slug":"/my-first-article/rabbitmq3/","title":"[RabbitMQ] RabbitMQ 실습 (2)","readingTime":{"text":"3 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}